💀NEW ART-The Hybrid Skeleton Room: “𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐋𝗼𝐬𝐭 𝐊𝐧𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭, 𝐰𝐡𝗼 𝐚𝐛𝐚𝐧𝐝𝗼𝐧𝐞𝐝 𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐩𝗼𝐬𝐢𝐭𝐢𝗼𝐧 𝗼𝐟 𝐛𝐞𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐊𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝗼𝐟 𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐋𝗼𝐬𝐭 𝐒𝗼𝐮𝐥 𝐊𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐝𝗼𝗺.“
---------------------------------
Known to be another half of The Lost Soul Kingdom royal family, The Lost Knight prefers being free and careless about his position running the kingdom. He spends most of his time searching for the hybrid creatures around the kingdom to bring them back to live.
Although physically, he is not there to rule the kingdom with The Lost Queen, they still share the same power which is to keep The Lost Soul Kingdom exist just by being alive. Because of that, their own soilders are be there to protect them.
[To be continued...]
